cogs.com/Mobb-Deep-The-Infamous/master/46381 ''The Infamous''] at [[Discogs]]\n*[http://www.rapreviews.com/archive/BTTL_theinfamous.html Album Review] at RapReviews.com\n*[http://www.acclaimedmusic.net/061024/A3580.htm Album Accolades and Ratings] at acclaimedmusic.net\n{{Mobb Deep}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Infamous, The}}\n[[Category:Mobb Deep albums]]\n[[Category:1995 albums]]\n[[Category:Albums produced by Havoc (musician)]]\n[[Category:Albums produced by Q-Tip (musician)]]\n[[Category:Loud Records albums]]\n[[Category:RCA Records albums]]\n", "name_user": "Blackjays1", "label": "safe", "comment": "\u2192\u200eRecording and production", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Infamous"}
